Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好有錢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼概念 不過應該跟這漫畫的作者差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:12.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我真的有做黑幫的才能 在現實中也能賺到這個數目的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人生去向的煩惱什麼的一下子就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搶劫銀行 日本 方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個國家搶劫銀行可行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:28.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:30.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賬戶之間的賬款來往幾乎都是電子化的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,銀行內部存有的最多就幾百萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這個國家有搶劫銀行的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那他只是個被電影或遊戲毒害的傻瓜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜而已…傻瓜而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.13,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord1\an9\c&H73DC65&\3c&H083B41&}被遊戲{\c&HDD107D&}毒{\c&H73DC65&}害的{\c&H22E9EF&}傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:42.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現實中做不到的事在遊戲裡做得到 僅此而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.21,0:06:50.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼明明有戰爭遊戲了卻還存在戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:58.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下床了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:08.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:12.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是反過來看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒過來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,8點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:21.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 真的糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上學路上沒出什麼問題的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全能輕鬆趕上…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:34.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不才4點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒 你在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有蟑螂出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼在換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變身來給自己打氣之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:52.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒…你…真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是真的在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:56.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不去學校了去下醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以不去醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:13.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠 沒想到居然把鍾看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:18.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在要面對一個很大的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:19.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡還是不睡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.18,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(473.6,343.6)\b0\c&H492216&\3c&HCAB8C7&}睡還是不睡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:29.29,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs85\blur5\fad(450,0)\fn@方正大黑_GBK\frz270.3\c&H7A2442&\3c&HDDD4D7&\b0\pos(198.4,338.8)}睡眠深度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為剛才的鬧劇搞得現在完全清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:28.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在睡覺的話就必須在深度睡眠的時候醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很難被鬧鐘的聲音叫醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:36.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至在遊戲裡槍戰中都能睡著叫不醒的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:41.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看那樣子媽媽也可能真的不會來叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}媽媽：&*@#%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.74,qianxu-staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,400)\bord3\fs60\fn@方正大黑_GBK\b0\c&HE4E7E4&\3c&HACAEB0&\frz284.3\pos(460.8,322.8)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.70,qianxu-staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(250,350)\fs60\fn@方正大黑_GBK\b0\c&HE4E7E4&\3c&HACAEB0&\frz273.4\pos(624,207.6)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.23,qianxu-staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(250,0)\fs60\fn@方正大黑_GBK\b0\c&HE4E7E4&\3c&HACAEB0&\frz273.4\pos(620.8,199.6)}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:44.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候 考慮最壞的情況的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.76,qianxu-huamian1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs150\blur2\bord0\c&HEFF0EC&\}去睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 完全睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天沒請假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同學對中午才回校的人有異常敏銳的第六感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.35,qianxu-huamian1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs150\blur2\bord0\c&HEFF0EC&\}不睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 其實昨晚沒怎麼睡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:08.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊 不難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:09.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:10.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很輕盈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:16.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就隨便說說 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:19.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣 都想儘量避免在班級裡顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平穩的學園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,經常就從這種細小的事情開始崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天在神社那碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:48.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和平常一樣的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對別遲到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒她用不著這麼強調吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我從沒遲到過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 早上四點半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:10:00.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒這發消息的時間真的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是遊戲嗎 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:05.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有好好睡覺嗎 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:08.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？小千緒先來真少見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:23.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神明保佑這個變態不是我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:41.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 睡了個好覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓真奈菜叫醒我作戰 成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的像那個樣子一直睡著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是顯眼得不得了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為遊戲想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:00.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要最終不暴露身份就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.13,0:11:06.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像頭一陣一陣地疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼 疼 超疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:11.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為睡眠不足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:16.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熬夜真是最難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:17.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 最終不暴露的話就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不暴露的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}早上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不暴露的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}給我起來 你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒的通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:36.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}如果有了7億的話你會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}哈？ 7億？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯 昨天弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在遊戲裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:43.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,篠塚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:44.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,篠塚你 拿到7億會怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說存起來的話就太沒新意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:55.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會被認為是個無聊的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要說點有幽默感的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:01.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 我 我會交稅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 自治體的預算增加了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,社會福利也會更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:11.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很有篠塚風格的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:11.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:18.18,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,750)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1616.8,854.267)}汗腺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 本週的特輯
Comment: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,/想詳細了解！！（左）
Comment: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,/在夏天來臨之前（右）
Comment: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,/夏天的氣味特輯（中）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:20.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人在意！身體的氣味問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我沒什麼關…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有注意到自己體臭的人也很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs100\blur1.5\bord0.5\c&H151124&\3c&H5868A3&\4c&H2F575D&\pos(451.2,346.4)}你也可能是{\shad8\fn方正大黑_GBK\4c&H3FFFFE&}狐臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.38,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\bord0\c&H090D0C&\3c&H6658DC&\4c&H2F575D&\pos(1496,431.2)}沒有自覺症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.38,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\bord0\c&H090D0C&\3c&H6658DC&\4c&H2F575D&\pos(1436.8,669.6)}有自覺症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.38,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\bord0\c&H090D0C&\3c&H6658DC&\4c&H2F575D&\pos(1320,900)}其他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到體臭的話大家經常認為是男性的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其實女性中有此煩惱的人也在增加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:43.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在接下來的季節裡大家大多會清爽地出門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入預防紫外線的對策的各位女性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:48.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有意想不到的奇怪方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:01.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不臭…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪倒是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:04.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs70}註：臭（臭い）和奇怪（きな臭い）都有臭い這個音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天 電視上在放跟體臭有關的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那東西自己是察覺不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:15.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒你能幫我確認下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不 你沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:24.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒氣味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:34.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我因為很不安都睡不著覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人類也是動物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:41.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在意過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:43.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小千緒你也讓我聞聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:47.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:49.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你要來這手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:51.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,參考 只是參考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 很害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也跟你一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:57.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜你擅自要我聞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:58.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:02.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺開始不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼招式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就動不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼情況 剛才那股強烈的野獸臭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子 還在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:36.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 很普通…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:38.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是足以把鼻子撕裂的味道什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:45.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到小千緒居然有這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼至今為止都沒注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:56.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們倆從小就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時起鼻子已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:00.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才 我可能全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:07.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小千緒變得執著於中下層
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:11.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在無意識中變得不敢在人前表現自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}話說 來開個派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然還是中止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因為體質問題受了很多傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:30.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明一直都在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 誒 為什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:39.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正好喉嚨渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:47.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？等下 都在一起也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:51.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她的問題也影響了我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一說我好像有點印象…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:58.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班上跟我處得不錯的牧山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:02.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得他明明絕對是對我有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:06.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不知道什麼時候開始和超級土的女生在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:09.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牧山的本命一定是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我有其他喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:17.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同班的野野村嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:19.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牧山你不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\pos(1036.8,988)}              gibier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 那個人是野味肉的好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs70}註：gibier是法語詞彙，指野生鳥獸的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:32.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野…野味肉是那個有野獸臭的四眼女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對 關係非常好 在女生間很有名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你和野野村交往了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:44.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牧山你可能也會被傳染吧 野味臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:52.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好險 我也差點被孤立了 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦 我也是擔心你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:00.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小 千 緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 你的情緒怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎麼了 發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:05.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:09.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 都怪野味肉 我的現充生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 不過 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你從剛剛就怪怪的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜沒事的啦 你不會臭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啦 野味肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:28.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到野味肉至今為止 還有以後的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好臭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:40.21,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此 我也 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡野味肉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:53.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…野味肉是指野獸的肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她以為吃了很臭的肉自己也會被傳染氣味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是傻逼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:06.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要一直陪在野味肉身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:09.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是指要成為獵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一直在你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.78,0:18:16.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓你繼續…給世界添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:19.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小雪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:23.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然叫你不好意思 不過真奈菜突然有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你能過來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 在叫小雪過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:36.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓不會說謊的誠實的好孩子來告訴你這殘酷的現實更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,審判之日快來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪好快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒這種事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:53.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這個人 是微笑的死神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你來了呢 Death Scythe細川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs70}註：Death Scythe：死神鐮刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:00.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.61,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 我有一件務必要請你確認下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後希望你能說出真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:12.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不臭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:15.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:20.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪不用顧慮哦 誠實點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 因為我不會說謊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那讓我也聞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的誒 不臭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不臭呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:39.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過剛才確實聞到了強烈的野獸臭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.61,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來好像從剛才開始就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:48.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭 什麼啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子沒裂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來出門之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣啦 那裡很癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是球普的唾液啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}狗狗的嘴巴有那麼臭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不…因為我家狗的牙齒不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:16.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 全都是狗狗的錯 千緒是沒味道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 野味肉不存在於這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:28.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…為什麼牧山沒有選擇我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去便利店借下廁所擦一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:32.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:38.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個你認不認識我們班上的牧山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 健介嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:42.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直接叫名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像最近交到女朋友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:51.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實有點在意他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你還沒告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:58.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:00.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.77,0:21:04.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,健介意外地還是個顏控呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Death Scythe細川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:14.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是殘酷的天使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:21.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對於顏控的牧山來說我是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒被打擊真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聞聞聞 嗅嗅嗅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃前輩是什麼味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:38.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:39.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了突然間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師你也是 旁邊一直有女生在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要注意下氣味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:52.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我對於努力著的大叔的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:53.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會討厭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:57.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔…
Comment: 0,0:21:58.96,0:23:29.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的千緒的通學路是由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:36.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「僅此一種能幹的方法」和「小雪一絲不掛」兩部分組成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:37.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:40.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦啦最終話
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----EDCN------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.07,0:22:20.04,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}回家路上說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:23.50,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}就這麼投入其中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:26.79,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}在好像很長的這一小段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:30.03,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}內心深處便會怦然一動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:33.35,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}雖然是理所當然的見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:36.66,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}但是每天卻非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:43.32,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}歡笑的時候 生氣的時候 都想全力碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:49.13,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不想說再見的感覺是想要隱藏起來的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.51,0:22:55.30,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}在回家之前就是上學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:22:57.51,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}明天再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:02.33,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不是你的話不就開始不了不是嗎 你說對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.67,0:23:08.75,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}無法見面的時間 為什麼總是感覺有所欠缺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:10.80,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}明天再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:15.75,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}和你一起的話無聊的一天也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.03,0:23:19.34,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}一如既往的景色 就由我們來破壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:23.16,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,500)}然後循環現在七色之路
